text: Jeannot Ahoussou-Kouadio (born 6 March 1951Official CV at government website .) is an Ivorian politician. He was Prime Minister of Ivory Coast from March 2012 to November 2012. ==References== ==Other websites== *Article (French) Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Ivory Coast
